posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Cutting edge fitness studio with cardio, strength training, Fitness On Demand and yoga studio', '-Summer kitchen pavilion including grills, pizza oven and refrigeration', '-Porcelain tile tub and shower surrounds', "-Spacious 9' ceilings", '-Whirlpool appliance package including French door with bottom freezer in stainless steel refrigerator', '-Electric car charging stations', '-Chef-caliber kitchens featuring 48-inch cabinets', '-Bike repair shop and interior bike storage', '-Modern one, two and three bedroom residences', '-Controlled access building with covered garage parking', '-Dacora rocker switches and USB outlets in the living room and bedrooms', '-Washer and dryer in every residence', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
